  "title": "Scaffolding tooling for new instantsearch.js projects",
  "body": "Would be nice to have a tool to bootstrap a new instantsearch.js. Simple command line stuff like `instantsearch new` that would ask a few questions (not mandatory in the beginning) : \n- name of the project\n- which css framework to use : bootstrap / foundation / none\n- which build system : browserify / webpack / simple html (use script from jsDeliver)\n",
